Lively interview and conversation in Berlin's Supermarkt, conducted by Elia Kagel and Thomas Doennebrink in March 2018. A second follow-up recording will focus on the required personal, cultural and spiritual transformations.

=Description=

"Michel Bauwens of the P2P Foundation visiting Berlin for some events of www.meetup.com/PlatformCoop-Berlin and the Freelancer Platform Cooperative http://smart-de.org/ in conversation with Ela Kagel & Thomas Dönnebrink talking about Commons and the undergoing and necessary transformations on the systemic, organisational and personal level."


